title: Australia Home Ownership Rate
description: Home Ownership Rate in Australia decreased to 66 percent in 2020 from 66.20 percent in 2018. Home Ownership Rate in Australia averaged 69.15 percent from 1966 until 2020, reaching an all time high of 71.40 percent in 1966 and a record low of 66 percent in 2020. This page provides the latest reported value for - Australia Home Ownership Rate - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Australian Bureau of Statistics
